WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.680 align:middle line:10%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:04.680 align:middle line:10%
>> Technology has made life
easier and more convenient

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:06.030 align:middle line:10%
for people.

00:00:06.030 --> 00:00:10.290 align:middle line:10%
But as artificial intelligence
replaces our human interactions

00:00:10.290 --> 00:00:13.410 align:middle line:10%
and measures our
deepest emotions,

00:00:13.410 --> 00:00:17.480 align:middle line:10%
is artificial intelligence
becoming too human?

00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:19.807 align:middle line:90%
This is Gaia News.

